description: Wheels On Fire is bringing the heat to the Denver streets in their custom-designed truck, complete with a blazing wood fired oven and mouthwatering selection of delicious pizzas, succulent Cuban sandwiches, and other specialities, all of which you’ll find yourself passionately loving. With healthy, local ingredients, as well as vegetarian and gluten-free options, these tasty Neapolitan pizzas and savory Latin street foods make for the perfect treat at any kind of event; festivals, weddings, corporate lunches, and more!
name: Wheels On Fire
